# SuperSpace Base Knowledge

## Project Overview

**SuperSpace** is a modular, feature-based SaaS platform with:
- **Next.js 15** (App Router) + React 19
- **Convex** (real-time serverless database)
- **Clerk** (authentication & billing)
- **TypeScript** + **Zod** (type safety & validation)
- **shadcn/ui** + **Tailwind CSS v4** (UI components)

**Status (December 2025):**
- **19/19 Dynamic Menus** ✅ Complete
- **Universal Database** ✅ 7 views, 20+ properties, 721 tests
- **All Core Systems** ✅ CRM, CMS, Projects, Support, Accounting, HR, BI

**Key Innovation:** Truly modular features with zero hardcoding and 100% auto-discovery.

## Core Concepts

### 1. Modular Feature System

**Everything is a feature.** Each feature is self-contained:
- Has own UI, backend, tests
- Can have nested sub-features
- RBAC-enforced (permission checks on all operations)
- Audit-logged (all mutations tracked)

### 2. Auto-Discovery

**Zero manual registration.** Features are auto-discovered:
- Browser: `lib/features/registry.ts` (uses `import.meta.glob`)
- Node.js: `lib/features/registry.server.ts` (uses `glob.sync`)

### 3. Three-Tier Sharing Model

1. **Global Shared** (`frontend/shared/`, `convex/shared/`)
   - Used by ALL features
2. **Feature-Shared** (`{feature}/shared/`)
   - Used within ONE feature
3. **Local** (within feature folder)
   - Used in one place only

### 4. RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)

**Permission Hierarchy:**
- Owner (0) → Full control
- Admin (10) → Manage workspace
- Manager (30) → Manage content
- Staff (50) → Create content
- Client (70) → Limited access
- Guest (90) → Read-only

**Every Convex handler MUST check permissions.**

### 5. Audit Logging

**All mutations are logged** to `activityEvents` table for:
- Compliance
- Forensics
- Debugging

## Project Structure

```
frontend/
├── features/                    # All features (modular)
│   ├── {feature-slug}/
│   │   ├── config.ts           # Single Source of Truth
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   ├── features/            # Nested sub-features
│   │   ├── shared/              # Feature-specific shared
│   │   └── settings/            # Feature settings
│   └── ...
├── shared/                      # Global shared
│   ├── ui/                      # shadcn/ui components
│   ├── foundation/              # Core utilities
│   └── ...
└── lib/
    └── features/
        ├── registry.ts          # Browser auto-discovery
        └── registry.server.ts    # Node.js auto-discovery

convex/
├── features/                    # Mirror frontend
│   ├── {feature_slug}/
│   │   ├── queries.ts
│   │   ├── mutations.ts
│   │   ├── schema.ts
│   │   ├── features/            # Nested sub-features
│   │   └── shared/               # Feature-shared
│   └── ...
└── shared/                       # Global shared
    ├── permissions/
    ├── audit/
    └── utils/

tests/
└── features/                    # Feature tests
    └── {feature-slug}/
```

